Package net.nergi.misc.objects

Class LargeWholeNumber

Object
LargeWholeNumber
public class LargeWholeNumber
extends Object
A discount, bargain-bin version of BigInteger. Supports addition and multiplication. Currently does not support negative numbers. Made as an exercise, not to be used except for demo purposes.
